      "span_text": "In order to establish a basis for comparison, 10 g each of bovine serum albumin (BSA), HBP (described earlier ), lysozyme, and MIP-1␣ were pooled, dissolved in 1 ml of ultrapure water, and passed through a 1-ml HiTRAP heparin column, and the unbound material was collected."
